ed="T" n="0778b09"/><persName key="A010544">釋日照</persName>，姓<name>劉</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000042879"><anchor xml:id="beg0778sgsz5"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0778sgsz5"/>下</placeName>人也。家世豪盛，幼承<lb
ed="T" n="0778b10"/>庭訓，博覽經籍，復於《莊》、《老》，而宿慧發揮，思<lb
ed="T" n="0778b11"/>從釋子。即往<placeName key="PL000000042218">長安大興善寺</placeName><persName key="A010545">曇光<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>下，稟<lb
ed="T" n="0778b12"/>學納戒，傳受經法，靡所不精。因遊<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩嶽</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0778b13"/>問圓通之訣，欣然趨入。後遊<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>，登<placeName key="PL000000028930">昂頭<lb
ed="T" n="0778b14"/>峯</placeName>，直拔蒼翠，便有終焉之志。庵居二十載，<lb
ed="T" n="0778b15"/>屬<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date><persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>毀教，<persName key="A010544">照</persName>深入巖窟，飯栗飲流<lb
ed="T" n="0778b16"/>而延喘息。<date from-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name></date><persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>重興佛法，率徒六十<lb
ed="T" n="0778b17"/>許人還就<placeName key="PL000000028930">昂頭山</placeName>舊基，結苫蓋，構舍宇。復<lb
ed="T" n="0778b18"/>居一十五年，學人波委。<date notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21" key="j20355242040147" notAfter-iso="+0873-08-18"><name>咸通</name>中</date>示滅，春秋一<lb
ed="T" n="0778b19"/>百八歲。至<date key="j20359692035969" when-iso="+0862-03-11">三年二月三日</date>入塔，立碑存焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0778b20"/>天下謂其禪學為<persName key="A010544">昂頭照</persName>是歟。</p>
